				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The difference between them is because Water is a rogue class instead of warrior class like Air and Earth.  
<br />

<br />
Air and Earth will KICK and BASH mobs.  This seems to be the major cause of the push.  Water does not kick or bash, but instead BACKSTABS. 
<br />

<br />
So if a raid leader complains about pet push often, try getting all the magicians to use water pets to reduce the push.  However, it has also been my experience that all the PC melee types are the ones pushing way to much, and I can't control them like I do my pet. <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="wink" border="0" /><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4796" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: #FF0000"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: normal">Lord Zacatac Soulwanderer</a></span></span></span>
