				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The best thing to do when the RL is complaining about pet push is to put the pets in guard mode *near* the mob.  When the mob gets pushed around and start to cry foul in /raid, simply tell them in /raid that your pet was on guard and wasn't attacking-- it was the melee that was pushing the mobs, not you.  A smart raid leader will figure it out and drop the discussion.  Let's just hope you don't have a stupid raid leader ..<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=653282" target=_blank>Casala</a>
